# TypeScript & React

- Functional components + hooks only; no class components
- Strict types; never use `any`
- Coordinates: `{ latitude: number; longitude: number }`
- Timestamps: ISO 8601 UTC strings
- Offline-first: optimistic updates with TanStack Query

## Lists & media (mobile)

- FlatList/FlashList for lists > 10 items (not ScrollView)
- `expo-image` over React Native `Image`
- Lazy-load media in lists; paginate API results (20 per page)
